{"title":"中俄友谊之歌","authors":["陈昊苏"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":7,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中俄友谊之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈昊苏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风浩荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在辽阔的田野放飞和平的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋色陶然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在繁华的城乡奏响友谊的乐章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情的挚爱献给两国母亲河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的伏尔加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄伟的黄河长江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏夜清凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向每一个角落传递和平的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬日温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向每一间小屋播洒友谊的阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真诚的祝福直达天涯海角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾的南海潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边的北冰洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友啊朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝愿平等信任地久天长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友啊朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝愿百年友谊壮丽辉煌。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}